LAGOS – Airtel Nigeria has announced that it is offering new customers on its network N1,000 bonus upon activation of their lines as well as 800% bonus every time they recharge their lines with airtime worth N100 and above. The new offer, which is christened Ovajara, is the default tariff plan for customers who are acquiring an Airtel SIM for the first time. After registering and activating their newly purchased SIM cards, customers will be automatically on-boarded on the Ovajara plan and will be rewarded instantly with the N1,000 activation bonus. Existing customers on the network can also enjoy 800% bonus on every recharge above N100 after activating the Ovajara plan by dialing *544#. Godfrey Efeurhobo, Chief Commercial Officer, Airtel Nigeria, while commenting on the new value offering, said the company is excited to welcome new customers on its network with a robust, innovative and affordable plan that will empower them to constantly stay connected with friends, family, business and social circles. “Airtel is always exploring opportunities to significantly improve the personal and professional productivity of our customers as well as make life better and more fun for them.”